'''泰勒·艾倫·格拉斯諾'''（{{lang-en|Tyler Allen Glasnow}}，{{bd|1993年|8月23日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟投手，目前效力於坦帕灣光芒。他先前曾效力過匹茲堡海盜。

==職業生涯==
===匹茲堡海盜===
[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，格拉斯諾在第5輪被海盜隊選走。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/preps/post/_/id/9069/la-north-pirates-pick-harts-tyler-glasnow-in-fifth-round-of-mlb-draft|title=LA North: Pirates pick Hart's Tyler Glasnow in fifth round of MLB draft|work=ESPN.com|accessdate=June 20, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304021136/http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/preps/post/_/id/9069/la-north-pirates-pick-harts-tyler-glasnow-in-fifth-round-of-mlb-draft|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年，格拉斯諾在3A先發20場，防禦率僅1.87，並送出133次三振。<ref name=returns>{{cite web |last=Berry |first=Adam |url=https://www.mlb.com/pirates/news/tyler-glasnow-returns-to-rotation-from-bullpen/c-203147964 |title=Tyler Glasnow returns to rotation from bullpen | Pittsburgh Pirates |publisher=Mlb.com |date=January 20, 2016 |accessdate=April 2, 2018 |archive-date=2018-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180402101556/https://www.mlb.com/pirates/news/tyler-glasnow-returns-to-rotation-from-bullpen/c-203147964 |dead-url=no }}</ref>海盜隊也在7月7日讓他升上大聯盟，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/16843693/towering-tyler-glasnow-ready-fill-tall-order-pirates |title=Tyler Glasnow ready to fill a tall order for Pirates |publisher=Espn.go.com |date=July 7, 2016 |accessdate=April 2, 2018 |archive-date=2016-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712191238/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/16843693/towering-tyler-glasnow-ready-fill-tall-order-pirates |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他在生涯第二場先發就因為肩膀不適而提前退場。7月23日，他以後援投手身分重返大聯盟，並一直到9月25日才回到先發行列。<ref name=returns/>這年他吞下2敗，防禦率為4.24。

2017年，格拉斯諾僅入海盜隊的先發輪值。不過他在這年的控球不盡理想，首場先發僅投1.2局就送出5次保送狂失5分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yawkeytalk.com/tyler-glasnow-commanding-attention-for-the-wrong-reasons|title=Tyler Glasnow: Commanding Attention for the Wrong Reasons – Yawkey Talk|website=www.yawkeytalk.com|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711211904/http://www.yawkeytalk.com/tyler-glasnow-commanding-attention-for-the-wrong-reasons|dead-url=no}}</ref>他回到3A後先發12場，防禦率還是高達7.45。不過隨著他後面在3A的表現趨於穩定，他也在球季末回到大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/pirates-tyler-glasnow-optioned-to-triple-a-indianapolis/|title=Pirates' Tyler Glasnow: Optioned to Triple-A Indianapolis|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714054330/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/pirates-tyler-glasnow-optioned-to-triple-a-indianapolis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他僅拿下2勝7敗，防禦率7.69。<ref>{{cite web |last=Berry |first=Adam |url=https://www.mlb.com/pirates/news/tyler-glasnow-not-discouraged-after-tough-18/c-259152832 |title=Tyler Glasnow not discouraged after tough '18 | Pittsburgh Pirates |publisher=Mlb.com |date=January 20, 2016 |accessdate=April 2, 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706022201/https://www.mlb.com/pirates/news/tyler-glasnow-not-discouraged-after-tough-18/c-259152832 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年春訓，海盜隊決定讓格拉斯諾擔任球隊的後援投手。<ref>{{cite web |author=<<<=theobj.bylinetime>>> |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2018/03/21/pitching-coach-ray-searage-pirates-starting-rotation-bullpen-2018/stories/201803210221 |title='Oh, yes. Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes.' Ray Searage describes Tyler Glasnow's progress, other pitchers | Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |publisher=Post-gazette.com |date= |accessdate=April 2, 2018 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712035834/https://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2018/03/21/pitching-coach-ray-searage-pirates-starting-rotation-bullpen-2018/stories/201803210221 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===坦帕灣光芒===
2018年7月31日，海盜將格拉斯諾、[[奧斯汀·米多斯|奧斯汀·米多斯]]和一名日後指定球員交易至光芒，換得[[克理斯·亞契|克理斯·亞契]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24246116/chris-archer-traded-pittsburgh-pirates-tampa-bay-rays|title=Archer excited to join surging Pirates after trade|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2018-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804112121/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24246116/chris-archer-traded-pittsburgh-pirates-tampa-bay-rays|dead-url=no}}</ref>格拉斯諾到了新東家後直接加入球隊先發輪值中，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rays/news/tyler-glasnow-strikes-out-5-in-rays-debut/c-288427186|title=Tyler Glasnow strikes out 5 in Rays debut|website=MLB.com|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802162945/https://www.mlb.com/rays/news/tyler-glasnow-strikes-out-5-in-rays-debut/c-288427186|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他先發11場比賽，防禦率4.20。

2019年開季，格拉斯諾投出5勝0敗，防禦率1.75的成績。他也獲選為美聯4月份單月最佳投手。5月10日，他因為手臂拉傷而進入傷兵名單。他一直到9月份才回歸球場。該年他拿下6勝1敗，防禦率1.78。
